      • getGroundCoverLayers

        List<GroundCoverLayer> getGroundCoverLayers()
        Gets a mutable ordered list of GroundCoverLayers. These layers will be applied to the base terrain during the generation phase starting at the topmost stone block in each column.
        Returns:
        The ground cover layers

      • getGenerationPopulators

        List<GenerationPopulator> getGenerationPopulators()
        Gets a mutable list of GenerationPopulators. These populators work strictly on a single chunk. They will be executed directly after the ground cover layers are applied. These generation populators are typically used to generate large terrain features, like caves and ravines.
        Returns:
        The generation populators

      • getPopulators

        List<Populator> getPopulators()
        Returns a mutable list of Populators specific to this biome. Changing this list will affect population of all new chunks.

        The populators
